00:28:09.956 --> 00:28:10.580
PROFESSOR: Yes.

00:28:10.580 --> 00:28:14.170
But imagine that I'm thinking
about the gas in this room

00:28:14.170 --> 00:28:16.590
and the interaction of
two oxygen molecules.

00:28:16.590 --> 00:28:20.290
So what I am saying is you
pick an oxygen molecule.

00:28:20.290 --> 00:28:22.940
There is interaction and
